        <a href="/ethanol-extraction-centrifuges-technical-comparison/">Ethanol Extraction Centrifuge</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/waste-oil-centrifuge/">Waste Oil De-sludging</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
