        <a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/">Municipal Wastewater</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/pyrolysis-oil-centrifuge/">Pyrolysis Sludge Separation</a>
